===Etymology 2===

====Verb====
'''ondergaan''' (''stress on "onder"'')
# To [[go down]]; to [[set]].
#: ''De zon ging onder.'' &mdash; The sun went down.
#: ''De ondergaande zon.'' &mdash; The setting sun.

